name: closeUnbilledPOReceipt

testSteps.description: Given that I'm logged into 'Unbilled PO Receipt' page

children.description: When i open page from sidebar menu: {Accounts Payable,Unbilled PO Receipts,Close Unbilled PO Receipt}

exception.message: Expected condition failed: waiting for visibility of element located by By.xpath: //div[@class = 'sidebar-menu-container'] (tried for 10 second(s) with 100 milliseconds interval)

testSteps.description: Then the 'Unbilled PO Receipts' page and its contents should show up
When I set the 'Supplier' to '115227'
When I click on 'Search' button
Then the 'Open Invoices' search result should show up
When I select first open invoices row
When I click 'Select CUPR Account' button
Then the 'Select CUPR Account' modal should show up
When I click first CUPR Account from modal
When I click modal 'Submit' button
When I click on 'Proceed' button
Then the 'CUPR Payment Successfully Created' modal should show up
When I click on 'Exit' button
Given that I'm logged into 'Review A/P Entries Payments' page
Then the'Payments' search page should show up
When I set the 'Batch Number' using saved value from an unbilled PO Receipt
When I click on 'Search' button
When I click on 'Delete' button
Then the 'Delete Manual Payment' modal should show up
When I click on modal 'Confirm' button

title: Close unbilled PO receipt
